             was indicted for <rs id="t18020428-136-off701" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18020428-136-off701" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18020428-136-off701" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18020428-136-cd702" type="crimeDate">26th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020428-136-off701 t18020428-136-cd702"></join>, two silver table-spoons, value 21s. a silver skewer, value 2s. and two four pronged silver forks, value 17s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18020428-136-victim946" type="victimName">
                        Thomas-Orbey 
                        Hunter
                     <interp inst="t18020428-136-victim946" type="surname" value="Hunter"></interp>
